              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>各种调查的误差来源，之前我倒是以为街头调查就比较平均了，没有考虑充分，受教了。</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-3.jpg"></div></div><p>不相关的数据，觉得自己对这方面的觉察力确实偏弱= =人傻</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-15.jpg"></div></div><p>最终总结章小笔记，要审慎考虑的五个问题和要点：</p><p>1、谁说的？</p><p>有意识的偏差（如刻意挑选数据、测量标准、测量方法）</p><p>无意识的偏差（迷信权威）</p><p>2、他是如何知道的？</p><p>样本是不是够大，观察值够不够多</p><p>3、遗漏了什么？</p><p>有没有对照组，是不是只给百分数掩饰样本量小，基数的选择是否合理，是否排除别的干扰因素来进行对比</p><p>4、是否有人偷换了概念？</p><p>搜集资料到形成结论过程中是否存在概念的偷换</p><p>5、这个资料有意义吗？</p><p>数据来源是否有参考价值，外推法的荒诞（各个时代时段情况不同，用经验得出的百分比去推测未来）</p><p></p><p></p><p>诶？这是一本自带笔记和重点的书啊……</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-4.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-5.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-6.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-7.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-8.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-10.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-12.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-13.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-14.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41992940-16.jpg"></div></div><p></p>
